      "content": "i mean i know i should see a doc but i hate going to the clinics here in mumbai it's such a hassle. do u think it's really that serious? it doesn't even feel like an asthma attack, just like i'm heavy or something. maybe i just need to take an extra puff of my ventolin more often?",
